a6367a9b4e20d32a5c1e27c2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nick Alexander \u003cnalexander@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1411654 - Part 5c: Work through ResourceUnused lint issues. r=mcomella\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 82rgLEEMQzG", "files": ["mobile/android/app/src/main/res/values-v11/themes.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/main/res/values-v13/search_styles.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/main/res/values-v16/search_styles.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/main/res/values/themes.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/photon/res/values-v11/styles.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/photon/res/values-v16/styles.xml", "mobile/android/app/src/photon/res/values/styles.xml", "mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/util/UnusedResourcesUtil.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "649e7aa405ca45b2fbf20bf07abd9e1c27cf4b30", "parents": ["c2e51b70519f5c905179bf7ce410b7e98e4cf2d4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nick Alexander \u003cnalexander@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1411654 - Post: Cull unused variables; guard more with MOZ_BUILD_MOBILE_ANDROID_WITH_GRADLE. r=maliu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8EGzVISIEQZ", "files": ["mobile/android/base/Makefile.in"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "113f1c4b95643c6dc29f74f704c8de0cace54a80", "parents": ["649e7aa405ca45b2fbf20bf07abd9e1c27cf4b30"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bobby Holley \u003cbobbyholley@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "servo: Merge #19753 - NoteDirtyElement optimizations (from bholley:notedirtyelement_optimizations); r=emilio\n\nhttps://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1398119\n\nSource-Repo: https://github.com/servo/servo\nSource-Revision: 1a8366598afdbf4de31dcbaf0d9585f7a8a5e7b4", "files": ["servo/components/style/gecko/generated/bindings.rs", "servo/ports/geckolib/glue.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "712a1f3ca9ef7dcf41056172ba892dde6f2edb4a", "parents": ["113f1c4b95643c6dc29f74f704c8de0cace54a80"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bobby Holley \u003cbobbyholley@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398119 - Add machinery to assert single-threadedness from geckolib. r=emilio\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9LBNm2h5Ct3\n", "files": ["layout/style/ServoBindings.cpp", "layout/style/ServoBindings.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "af26f7cb29cad6565a58f3be7a6f83c8ad443871", "parents": ["712a1f3ca9ef7dcf41056172ba892dde6f2edb4a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bobby Holley \u003cbobbyholley@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398119 - Rearrange NoteDirtyElement for faster bailouts on the same restyle root. r=emilio\n\nThis eliminates ~90% of the time spent in NoteDirtyElement on this testcase.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Lm5hf7QRiOK\n", "files": ["dom/base/Element.cpp", "dom/base/nsIDocument.h", "dom/base/nsIDocumentInlines.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dae0996220912b49d69d26759f6a1453abb7d530", "parents": ["af26f7cb29cad6565a58f3be7a6f83c8ad443871"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Tromey \u003ctom@tromey.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1255401 - fix values allowed for \"all\" property; r=heycam\n\nThe \"all\" property in the devtools CSS database included all possible\nproperty values; however only a few are truly appropriate.  This patch\nadds a special case for \"all\" to\nInspectorUtils::GetCSSValuesForProperty to fix this.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HEnrvCJylHI", "files": ["devtools/shared/css/generated/properties-db.js", "layout/inspector/InspectorUtils.cpp", "layout/inspector/tests/test_bug877690.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "52fbf0d6c18c0eda95b107d73af577093e80f9da", "parents": ["dae0996220912b49d69d26759f6a1453abb7d530"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Tromey \u003ctom@tromey.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1255401 - fix getCSSValuesForProperty result for \"quotes\" property; r=heycam\n\nIt seemed valid to simply set the expected variants in\nnsCSSPropList.h; other properties (e.g., align-content) do this as\nwell.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HVZGOofkwi1", "files": ["devtools/shared/css/generated/properties-db.js", "layout/inspector/tests/test_bug877690.html", "layout/style/nsCSSPropList.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1572cddc9e46271f000627a6f0e259885bf069bc", "parents": ["52fbf0d6c18c0eda95b107d73af577093e80f9da"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Csoregi Natalia \u003cncsoregi@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 4 changesets (bug 712130) for Android autofocus failures and for failing browser_formdata.js. on a CLOSED TREE\n\nBacked out changeset e7738f07edae (bug 712130)\nBacked out changeset 3774e90777a7 (bug 712130)\nBacked out changeset a3cffbfc8395 (bug 712130)\nBacked out changeset ba6c2fff9fd5 (bug 712130)", "files": ["dom/base/nsDocument.cpp", "dom/base/nsDocument.h", "dom/base/nsFocusManager.cpp", "dom/base/nsIDocument.h", "dom/html/nsGenericHTMLElement.cpp", "layout/base/PresShell.cpp", "layout/reftests/bugs/712130-1-ref.html", "layout/reftests/bugs/712130-1.html", "layout/reftests/bugs/712130-2-ref.html", "layout/reftests/bugs/712130-2.html", "layout/reftests/bugs/reftest.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "96acd76fdf71cfa850a55bc5b6340267f5830234", "parents": ["1572cddc9e46271f000627a6f0e259885bf069bc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Tromey \u003ctom@tromey.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1255384 - fix getCSSValuesForProperty for counter-*; r=heycam\n\nThis bug notes that getCSSValuesForProperty does not mention the\n\"none\" value for counter-increment and counter-reset.  This fixes the\nproblem by mentioning the variants in the entries in nsCSSPropList.h.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HpZIMIIejHc", "files": ["devtools/shared/css/generated/properties-db.js", "layout/inspector/tests/test_bug877690.html", "layout/style/nsCSSPropList.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "de312c964b3a6b6a864f4ea987a61b820dae7ac1", "parents": ["96acd76fdf71cfa850a55bc5b6340267f5830234"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bryce Van Dyk \u003cbvandyk@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1429765 - Extend lifetime of MediaRecorder telemetry probes. r=chutten,liuche\n\nExtend lifetime of MEDIA_RECORDER_RECORDING_DURATION,\nMEDIA_RECORDER_TRACK_ENCODER_INIT_TIMEOUT_TYPE, and\nSCALARS_MEDIARECORDER.RECORDING_COUNT telemetry probes. This allows continued\nmonitoring of MediaRecorder usage in the wild. See Bug 1400757 for the original\nintroduction of these probes.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FzM2Awhv25H", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/Histograms.json", "toolkit/components/telemetry/Scalars.yaml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6e299e057fd4396cd4900c82336df2c2c511fce4", "parents": ["de312c964b3a6b6a864f4ea987a61b820dae7ac1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dustin J. Mitchell \u003cdustin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1407163: raise exceptions with HTTP error info; r=glandium\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: B3MvsZDpj9a", "files": ["python/mozbuild/mozbuild/mach_commands.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d40da09bed641cb7638d1e9cc96d6ab1edda8189", "parents": ["6e299e057fd4396cd4900c82336df2c2c511fce4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike de Boer \u003cmdeboer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1401678 - Proxy nsISound::beep() and nsISound::play() calls from the content process to the parent process and beep away there. r=bkelly\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: J7NwDeVYvQw", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.h", "dom/ipc/PContent.ipdl", "widget/moz.build", "widget/nsContentProcessWidgetFactory.cpp", "widget/nsSoundProxy.cpp", "widget/nsSoundProxy.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "19af171d77189ac5a35fd2d471b78884d764bc6a", "parents": ["d40da09bed641cb7638d1e9cc96d6ab1edda8189"], "tags": []}, {"author": "ffxbld", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug, Automated HSTS preload list update from host bld-linux64-spot-324 - a=hsts-update", "file