f5cf32327b5bdfeb66e3e58382428b2bc8", "parents": ["19af171d77189ac5a35fd2d471b78884d764bc6a", "f5b4481c9fd50becb35cef02b599198b766fb1bb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Martin Giger \u003cmartin@humanoids.be\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387624 - Fix datalist popups in extension options r=mixedpuppy\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9w7Hhv5Fh4n", "files": ["toolkit/components/satchel/AutoCompletePopup.jsm", "toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/extensions.js", "toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/extensions.xul", "toolkit/themes/shared/extensions/extensions.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1c4243ce6d43af3b737b9c1590a9f33f684c784d", "parents": ["9da066f5cf32327b5bdfeb66e3e58382428b2bc8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Zibi Braniecki \u003czbraniecki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1389384 - Batch l10n mutations to one per paint. r=mossop\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: AbclA2lzTfT", "files": ["intl/l10n/DOMLocalization.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "67f5e518f5751d7d037db95d5d7e705d04d1752e", "parents": ["1c4243ce6d43af3b737b9c1590a9f33f684c784d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh+mozilla@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1430270 - Disable ccache in hazard builds. r=nalexander\n\nI don't intend to install ccache in the Debian build images. Hazard\nbuilds are the only builds running on the desktop-build image still\nusing ccache somehow, and that gains them nothing, since the ccache\ndirectory is not set to a cached directory on taskcluster, meaning\nthe build always starts with an empty cache. If anything, this currently\nmakes the build slower.\n\nEventually, those builds should be able to use sccache, once the\nnecessary setup moves out of mozconfig.cache.", "files": ["taskcluster/scripts/builder/build-haz-linux.sh", "taskcluster/scripts/builder/hazard-analysis.sh", "taskcluster/scripts/builder/setup-ccache.sh"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7902f47451a1d405e4123631be7b6c432bfd2092", "parents": ["67f5e518f5751d7d037db95d5d7e705d04d1752e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmconley@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1430072 - Make the TabParent's default cached value for the DocShell active state be false again. r=mystor\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: AMAJgD8n0Lp", "files": ["dom/ipc/TabParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "373575d2ce7192a8ca778591c3ce6bbbbbb19d53", "parents": ["7902f47451a1d405e4123631be7b6c432bfd2092"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Tolfsen \u003cato@sny.no\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1430119 - Fix API documentation in testing/marionette/server.js. r=maja_zf\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: KEPTCkrdqOr", "files": ["testing/marionette/server.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c913f802e71a5808c0d457c16e55bcfaa2f5b43a", "parents": ["373575d2ce7192a8ca778591c3ce6bbbbbb19d53"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmconley@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1420902 - Bail out of RemoteSizeShellTo if the docShell has gone away. r=mystor\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4X3bfSeHGiA", "files": ["dom/ipc/TabChild.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eb8c89d823a6036963332c14e878ff48292c5915", "parents": ["c913f802e71a5808c0d457c16e55bcfaa2f5b43a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Byron Campen [:bwc] \u003cdocfaraday@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1425621 - Part 1: Test-case for removeTrack and MediaStream.onremovetrack. r=jib\n\n  Also, expects onmute to happen before SRD resolves, even for offers.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 2ibQKDfyHYH", "files": ["dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_peerConnection_transceivers.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ecc116e85fb208529894051ae2c0d7f0420151b2", "parents": ["eb8c89d823a6036963332c14e878ff48292c5915"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Byron Campen [:bwc] \u003cdocfaraday@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1425621 - Part 