"Luke Crouch \u003clcrouch@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 587523 - strict-origin-when-cross-origin referer policy in pbmode r=valentin\n\nAdds new network.http.referer.defaultPolicy.pbmode pref which defaults to 2.\n\nWhen setting referrer from default policy, checks mLoadInfo OriginAttributes\nfor mPrivateBrowsingId \u003e 0 to detect PBM.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7SfNk0dO1rW", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/all.js", "netwerk/base/nsNetUtil.cpp", "netwerk/base/nsNetUtil.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/HttpBaseChannel.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "36474234a91822bf90d89f5fb67245b9dd2d5f6f", "parents": ["cac65d7b590f5121a73154a6e44bc662d8bd5ccd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Luke Crouch \u003clcrouch@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 587523 - rename referer.userControlPolicy to referer.defaultPolicy r=valentin\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: A2hkYfdTCR9", "files": ["dom/tests/mochitest/fetch/test_fetch_user_control_rp.html", "modules/libpref/init/all.js", "netwerk/base/nsNetUtil.cpp", "netwerk/base/nsNetUtil.h", "netwerk/test/mochitests/test_origin_header.html", "netwerk/test/unit/test_referrer.js", "netwerk/test/unit/test_referrer_policy.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "127b3aee4a44ad5cba661cc0f2d00988c368e0ed", "parents": ["36474234a91822bf90d89f5fb67245b9dd2d5f6f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Luke Crouch \u003clcrouch@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 587523: update test_referrer.js to include pbmode tests r=valentin\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FXUMi9Q3S3P", "files": ["netwerk/protocol/http/HttpBaseChannel.cpp", "netwerk/test/unit/test_referrer.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3259f30e0fd5b4b28db3145a989d70feaab66b3d", "parents": ["127b3aee4a44ad5cba661cc0f2d00988c368e0ed"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Luke Crouch \u003clcrouch@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 587523: update Fetch API referrer to check for private browsing pref r=valen