zing builds to use legacy and unsigned addons. r=froydnj, a=NPOTB", "files": ["browser/config/mozconfigs/linux64/nightly-fuzzing-asan"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "33d70d37011df8b107629cd8aca2e765729417ea", "parents": ["9571f24380c03d953c2d36dfdf28a480723ebe46"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Maja Frydrychowicz \u003cmjzffr@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1421878 - Reset Marionette's click state on document unload; r=whimboo, a=test-only\n\nThis makes more sense with the UIEvent spec and it should fix\nintermittent failures caused by extra dblclick events that arise\nfrom different tests polluting each other's state.\n\nFor the wdspec actions tests, the `test_actions_page`\nfixture is function-scoped, so the page is reloaded between\neach subtest.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HxPbMzYeXIV", "files": ["testing/marionette/event.js", "testing/marionette/listener.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fa6c5f94f937a55a22c6377fafcc4fcfc1aa0586", "parents": ["33d70d37011df8b107629cd8aca2e765729417ea"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daniel Holbert \u003cdholbert@cs.stanford.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1432202 - Slightly loosen the fuzzy annotation on reftest 84400-1.html to allow 3 mismatching pixels. a=test-only", "files": ["layout/reftests/bugs/reftest.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "68f206b648afc79e87bcd01e4d341498fa1794af", "parents": ["fa6c5f94f937a55a22c6377fafcc4fcfc1aa0586"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1429744 - Relax a test of StyleRuleAdded events to allow for the possibility that style rules could arrive before import rules. r=emilio, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: COIK852QzUm\n\nThe test also verifies that when an import rule event arrives, that the rule has a loaded stylesheet.", "files": ["layout/inspector/tests/chrome/test_parseStyleSheetObservers.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0a7b0fd5bf128263b4869d896909ce0b1deb14a9", "parents": ["68f206b648afc79e87bcd01e4d341498fa1794af"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Ritter \u003ctom@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1432009 - Fix MinGW build failure with d_write3.h. r=jfkthame, a=NPOTB\n\nBump mingw version to get the newest commit and do not include the\nun-needed dw-extras.h on MinGW (thanks Jacek!)\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: OjO93XHCxs", "files": ["gfx/thebes/gfxDWriteFontList.h", "taskcluster/scripts/misc/build-gcc-mingw32.sh"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3221e647134d970526ca63fa24cb3c5b3c4b4cb2", "parents": ["0a7b0fd5bf128263b4869d896909ce0b1deb14a9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Edan Reynolds \u003cedanreynolds@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1431394 - requestCompleteLog so mozprocess knows we're still alive for the long session. r=MattN, a=test-only", "files": ["browser/tools/mozscreenshots/head.js", "browser/tools/mozscreenshots/primaryUI/browser_primaryUI.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1544a22ca3134c8a7f6a9417296ecdfe6f0711bd", "parents": ["3221e647134d970526ca63fa24cb3c5b3c4b4cb2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike de Boer \u003cmdeboer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1411581 - Mochitest 'browser_615394-SSWindowState_events_undoCloseTab.js' leaks windows too frequently; rewrite the test and wait for the browser to load, before finishing up the test. r=mconley, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 6HFJTZP8tLB", "files": ["browser/components/sessionstore/test/browser_615394-SSWindowState_events_undoCloseTab.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9878e0378cadb2ac2c3e4a8a591b8eb127a965b1", "parents": ["1544a22ca3134c8a7f6a9417296ecdfe6f0711bd"], "tags": []}], "date": 1516732075, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8576": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "bran