=ritu\n\nWe now know that worker restarts are rather frequent and we've had reports that\nare certain to point at us forgetting to properly re-initialize the worker.\nThis takes care of this by factoring the init flow into its own method and setting\nthe flag when a failing worker is terminated.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: G5jccjxkBsF", "files": ["browser/components/sessionstore/SessionFile.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "aeb7a1482e4d9ecd0e4c40604c167e2dd287e19b", "parents": ["bcf52fbf84456bf8d0eb4bf85179275e4075bde5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike de Boer \u003cmdeboer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1427007 - Part 2: the SessionFile unit tests dependended on a very specific interaction between wipe() and read(), which changed in part 1. This fixes the tests up by making the dependency a bit more clear and explicit. r=Yoric a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: uoPx46cNL1", "files": ["browser/components/sessionstore/SessionFile.jsm", "browser/components/sessionstore/test/browser_backup_recovery.js", "browser/components/sessionstore/test/browser_upgrade_backup.js", "browser/components/sessionstore/test/unit/test_shutdown_cleanup.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b89f4d21c530d5ec7d2903350745843e1215b5a6", "parents": ["aeb7a1482e4d9ecd0e4c40604c167e2dd287e19b"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_59_0b10_BUILD3", "DEVEDITION_59_0b10_RELEASE", "FIREFOX_59_0b10_BUILD3", "FIREFOX_59_0b10_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1518693295, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "8712": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nfi -\u003e 78ccaa0daf55\ngu-IN -\u003e 9d48fcde1644\nit -\u003e f805d68a5020\nms -\u003e 2a1252484fb6\nnl -\u003e d7241f04191c\npl -\u003e 73390245084b\nsq -\u003e e0f16e95d0be\nsv-SE -\u003e 1138ab905b21\nur -\u003e 6bc66af6221e", "fi